    "why_we_launched_FyUjVB": {
      "type": "why-we-launched",
      "blocks": {
        "block_XNNkXF": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/image_3_2.webp",
            "head": "The Unspoken Truth: A Fiber Gap",
            "text": "<p><strong>95% of Americans are missing out on essential fiber from diverse whole foods. </strong>This isn't just a statistic; it's a silent challenge to our vitality. Fiber is the crucial fuel for your beneficial gut bacteria, actively nurturing a balanced microbiome (that includes your skin). Without it, we're not just missing a nutrient—we're missing the foundation for true flourish.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "decorative_svg": "shopify://shop_images/Group_72.webp"
          }
        },
        "block_VnGCtj": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1908474785.webp",
            "head": "For People, Planet, and Pure Pleasure.",
            "text": "<p>We're on a bold mission to intercept 100 million pounds of fresh produce trimmings—the rinds, skins, and cores—that would otherwise contribute to global food waste. This isn't just about sustainability; it's about transforming forgotten abundance into vital nourishment, creating a powerful ripple effect for both human health and the health of our planet.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false
          }
        },
        "block_wrCLbJ": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/jeni-homepage-mango.png",
            "head": "Crafted by a Tastemaker. Led by a Visionary.",
            "text": "<p>Floura is making fiber not just delicious, but an experience. With the same iconic flavor design that inspired the very tastes you love from Jeni's Splendid Ice Creams, our products are a testament to the power of a true tastemaker. Jeni Britton's vision ensures that every bar is a delightful step towards a more vibrant you.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "block_XNNkXF",
        "block_VnGCtj",
        "block_wrCLbJ"
      ],
      "name": "Why We Launched",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "Why We Launched"
      }
    },
